<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="eyebrow">Senior Backend Engineer · Go</div>
    <h1>Felipe Ascari</h1>
    <p>
      Started in desktop apps with Dataflex, writing logistics software for transportation companies
      when barely anyone outside niche ERP circles had heard of the language.
      Moved to Java for a decade, mostly in public accounting —
      municipal tax systems, fiscal documents, the kind of software that has to be right.
      Then back to logistics at Ambev, and eventually into fintech, where I've been since 2022.
      These days it's Go, distributed systems, and the occasional blockchain experiment.
      More than 15 years in, still finding new things to break and fix.
    </p>
